                  com.ibm.team.build.ant.task.WorkItemPublisherTask

public final class WorkItemPublisherTask
extends AbstractFilePublisherTask

Ant task to publish work item information to a build result. This task expects the filePath attribute to be set to the path to a change set file output from the TeamAcceptTask or the path to a file that contains the ids of work items to be published, one id per line. The path can be relative to the base directory of the build file or an absolute path.

Optional attributes are:
  • inputFileType - This flag indicates whether the filePath attribute indicates a change set file or a work item file. Valid values are "CHANGESET" and "WORKITEM". If this attribute is not specified, the task assumes the filePath attribute points to a changeset file.
See AbstractFilePublisherTask for other required and optional attributes.

Since:
0.5
